Package: OpenBlasThreads
Type: Package
Title: Miniature Package to Set Number of OpenBlasThreads
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-07-26
Author: Simon Fuller, with contributions from Claudia Beleites
Maintainer: Simon Fuller <simonfuller9@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Suggests: 
Description: Sets "set_openblas_num_threads" for linux systems with OpenBlas correctly installed. This function is currently only a dummy for Windows so no Windows capabilities are available as of yet. Please note: this assumes OpenBlas is installed in opt/openblas, as per the library recommendations. Otherwise alter the path given in Makevars.
